<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="name-n">name <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /neɪm/    美 /neɪm/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>名字；名称：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Sign</strong> your <strong>name</strong> here, please. 
请在这里签上你的名字。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-reputation">2.<strong>名声 (reputation)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The college <strong>has a good name for</strong> teaching languages.
这个学院的语言教学颇有名气。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>名人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some of the <strong>biggest names</strong> in the show business were at the party.
演艺界的一些大牌明星参加了聚会。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="by-the-name-of">by the name of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用语] 名叫…的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is a British athlete by the name of Tanni Grey Thompson. 
她是一名英国运动员，名叫坦妮·格雷·汤普森。</p><footer>2008 福建</footer></div>

<h3 id="in-the-name-of">in the name of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在…名下；以…的名义；代表 (in sb’s / sth’s name)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve booked a table in your name. 
我已经用你的名字预订了一张桌子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I arrest you in the name of the law. 
我依法逮捕你。</p></div>

<h3 id="make-a-name-for-oneself-make-ones-name">make a name (for oneself) / make one’s name</h3>
<p>1.<strong>成名；出名：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She first made her name as a writer of children’s books. 
她最初以写儿童读物成名。</p></div>

<h3 id="under-the-name-of">under the name of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>以…为别名</strong>  </p></div>